# VHS tape: fqxv top-level help
Output docs/images/help.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "FiraCode Nerd Font"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 760
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set LineHeight 1.2
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set MarginFill "#fe00fe"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Margin 20
Set BorderRadius 10

Type "fqxv --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s
